      <description>&lt;p&gt;Profile has many ApiResponses&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;def api_response
  order(&amp;lsquo;id desc&amp;rsquo;).first
end&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;makes multiple queirers n+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;use rails has_one :api_response -&amp;gt; order(&amp;lsquo;id desc&amp;rsquo;)
this searchs api_responses for profile_id and returns the first, we just need to make sure
we order for the one we want.&lt;/p&gt;
